 (MEND).<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref> The insurgent organization wreaks havoc on international oil companies operating in the <misfortune wordnetid="114475405" confidence="0.8">
