<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../889/158889.xml">
George Clooney</link></actor>
</person>
.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref> It also claimed the organization was considering a cease-fire after receiving an "appeal" by U.S. Senator <person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<senator wordnetid="110578471" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
